  <brief_title>A Safety, Efficacy and Tolerability Study of SEP-225289</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Study Examining The Safety, Efficacy, and Tolerability of SEP-225289 in Subjects With Major Depressive Disorder (Including Atypical and Melancholic Features)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
